{"type":null,"faqId":31861,"title":"系统休眠后，WLAN 是否会自动断开？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手机的 WLAN 连接策略默认为：在充电时，WLAN 会一直保持连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如需使 WLAN 一直保持连接，请参考如下步骤：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击或滑动 “WLAN” 后的开关至 “</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98979\" style=\"width:0.28541666in;height:0.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击“菜单 &gt; 高级设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98980\" style=\"width:5.164583in;height:2.4590278in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击“在休眠状态下保持 WLAN 连接”，然后勾选“始终”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98981\" style=\"width:5.165278in;height:3.6819444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98982\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6381","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287939000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":48,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"系统休眠,休眠,wifi,wifi 断开,wifi 关闭,网断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}